#

Cilantro Lime Chicken Bowls

$15.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

DinnerQuickPopularHealthy

Description

A vibrant bowl of cilantro lime chicken served over fluffy rice, topped with black beans, corn, and fresh avocado.

Ingredients

  • Chicken breasts: 2, boneless and skinless
  • Brown rice: 1 cup
  • Black beans: 1 can, drained and rinsed
  • Corn kernels: 1 cup, fresh or frozen
  • Avocado: 1, diced
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • Cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
